(50,	'marketplace.settings.landing_page.about_marketplace',	'<div style=\"width: 100%; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 30px;\"><h1 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); margin-bottom: 40px;\">How it works</h1><div style=\"width: 28%; float: left; padding-right: 20px;\"><img src=\"http://magento2.webkul.com/marketplace/pub/media/wysiwyg/landingpage/img-customize-seller-profile.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></div> <div style=\"width: 70%; float: left; text-align: justify;\"><h2 style=\"color: rgb(99, 99, 99); margin: 0px; font-size: 22px;\">Set up a customised store</h2> <p>Fresh-Net is an online marketplace that connects suppliers with buyers. The platform allows suppliers the ability to develop a fully customisable online store to advertise their brand and demonstrate their USPs. Add all relevant information for customers such as delivery requirements, minimum purchases, credit terms etc.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>We pride ourselves in supporting your business growth, that\'s why we have a support team ready to answer any of your queries, help open your store and even build your branding content such as shop front banners and promotions. All completely for free!</p></div></div> <div style=\"width: 100%; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 30px;\"><div style=\"width: 70%; float: left; padding-right: 20px; text-align: justify;\"><h2 style=\"color: rgb(99, 99, 99); margin: 0px; font-size: 22px;\">Add and Manage Products with Ease</h2> <p>Simply add your products to your online store. Manage pricing and push offers when necessary with the click of a button.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Track and manage inventory with simplicity via the online store, communicate directly with customers for items like delivery or credit terms.</p></div> <div style=\"width: 28%; float: left;\"><img src=\"http://magento2.webkul.com/marketplace/pub/media/wysiwyg/landingpage/img-add-unlimited-products.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></div></div> <div style=\"width: 100%; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 30px;\"><div style=\"width: 28%; float: left; padding-right: 20px;\"><img src=\"http://magento2.webkul.com/marketplace/pub/media/wysiwyg/landingpage/img-connect-to-your-social-profile.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></div> <div style=\"width: 70%; float: left;text-align: justify;\"><h2 style=\"color: rgb(99, 99, 99); margin: 0px; font-size: 22px;\">Build your Brand Presence</h2> <p>Build your brand presence by connecting your shop to social media. Enhance your presence online through pushed discounts, targeted adverts and much more.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>If you\'re stuck for ideas, Fresh-Net can help you build professional marketing content such as banners, logos and designs. We wan\'t your store to maximise your revenue so just contact our support centre to get more information on marketing your store.</p></div></div> <div style=\"width: 100%; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 30px;\"><div style=\"width: 70%; float: left; padding-right: 20px; text-align: justify;\"><h3 style=\"color: rgb(99, 99, 99); margin: 0px;\">Seamless Buyer Communication</h3> <p>Communicate with buyers at the click of a button. Put as much information on your site as possible to minimise questions, making sure you\'re using the messaging system for relationship building. Our support team can also help pick up any queries if required.</p></div> <div style=\"width: 28%; float: left;\"><img src=\"http://magento2.webkul.com/marketplace/pub/media/wysiwyg/landingpage/img-buyers-can-ask-a-question.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></div></div>',	'default',	'en',	NULL,	'2020-04-13 22:41:09'),
